{"tid":568240,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 一齊玩揭尾故！27","createTime":"2018-02-21T15:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T23:18:05.000Z","uid":136763,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4dddbca8a36364f53b6961b9593946bcace14368","tid":568240,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n馬田一早起床 感覺好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   連老闆 枝筆係？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個客送嘅 大客嚟 佢間公司唔錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中年肥佬？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你又知嘅 ？ 係呀 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無 好似見過啫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈哈 今晚公司party <br />\n啲高層都係度 你無得推㗎啦 早啲到呀 ！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗯？ 我枝筆呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一切正常？<br />\n<br />\n係  <br />\n<br />\n咁就好 我唔想傷及無辜 <br />\n<br />\n咪住 情況有變 <br />\n<br />\n咁 ， 有殺錯無放過 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解咁㗎 ！ ？ 點解會唔同咗㗎！？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次個故有啲長<br />\n場景都有變化<br />\n有連老闆啦終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧 五頁內"},{"pid":"f80dde1224ecf1e7fde712d82d7ad4b855301c9d","tid":568240,"uid":137503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179dc7ff326852ff12b865803068de662ee8e193","tid":568240,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80dde1224ecf1e7fde712d82d7ad4b855301c9d","tid":568240,"uid":137503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac